Package projektarbeit.immobilienverwaltung.model

Class Wohnung

java.lang.Object
projektarbeit.immobilienverwaltung.model.Wohnung
@Entity public class Wohnung extends Object
Represents a property (Wohnung) entity with details about the property such as address, size, number of rooms, and amenities. This entity is mapped to the database table 'wohnung'.

    • setMieter

      public void setMieter(Mieter mieter)
      Sets the Mieter for this Wohnung.

      If the Wohnung is already associated with a Mieter, it will be removed from the current Mieter's list of Wohnungen. Then, the new Mieter will be assigned to this Wohnung, and this Wohnung will be added to the new Mieter's list of Wohnungen.

      Parameters:
      mieter - The new Mieter to be assigned to this Wohnung. If null, the Wohnung will be disassociated from any Mieter.

    • getFormattedAddress

      public String getFormattedAddress()
      Returns the formatted address of the Wohnung (apartment).

      The address format includes the country, postal code, city, street, and house number. If the address or postal code object is null, it returns "Keine Adresse".

      Returns:
      A formatted string representing the address of the Wohnung, or "Keine Adresse" if the address or postal code object is null.
